    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a benchmark of atmospheric performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry using OEM bushings to preserve its legendary turn-in response. The exterior retains its factory deep-gloss finish with no signs of clear coat failure, while the interior features immaculate Nappa leather and functional electronics. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key specimen for the serious driving purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
